This will reply to you when you react with the "â¤ï¸" emoji to your initial command message:

```js
client.command({
  name: "awaitCmdReaction",
  code: `
  React with "â¤ï¸" for a surprise! 
  $awaitCmdReactions[$authorID;10s;â¤ï¸;awaitedCommandExample;Whoops! You didn't react in time..]
