This will return the ID of every server member and log it in your console:

```javascript
client.command({
  name: "awaitData",
  code: `
  $forEachMember[1s;{ "members": "$membersCount" };returnMembers;]
  `
});

client.awaitedCommand({
  name: "returnMembers",
  code: `
  $log[ $authorID , is one out of $awaitData[members] members ]
  `
});
```

This will reply to you when you react with the "â¤ï¸" emoji to the bot's message:

```js
client.command({
  name: "awaitMessageReactions",
  code: `
  React with "â¤ï¸" for a surprise! 
  $awaitMessageReactions[$channelID;$messageID;$authorID;10s;â¤ï¸;awaitedcommandexample;Whoops! You didn't react in time..]
